                        <summary>
                            
                            <p>On the east wall of the <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa</hi> in front of the central shrine in the Chandramauḷīśvara temple.</p>						
                            
                            <p>Vikramachōḷa. Year 5: 1122-23 A.D.</p>						
                            
                            <p>This record commences with <hi rend="italic">Pūmādu puṇara</hi>, etc., the <hi rend="italic">praśasti</hi> of the king.</p>						
                            
                            <p>It mentions Arumbākkiḻān Araiyan of Maṇavil in Maṇavil-kōṭṭam in Jayaṅ goṇḍachōḻa-maṇḍalam.</p>						
                            
